'''Yin Wood Rabbit''', also known as '''Otsubō''' (乙卯, Kinotō, Otsuboku no Usagi, Otsuboku no U, Itsubō), is one of the elements in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
It is the 52nd combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Jia Yin|ja|甲寅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and preceding {{ill|Bing Chen|ja|丙辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Yi|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Wood (Wu Xing)|ja|木|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Mao|ja|卯|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} also corresponds to Yin Wood, making it a {{ill|Bihe (Five Elements)|ja|比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|4=el|5=Ου Σιν|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} combination.
== Years of the Yin Wood Rabbit == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 55 are considered Yin Wood Rabbit years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Wood Rabbit''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[55]] * [[115]] * [[175]] * [[235]] * [[295]] * [[355]] * [[415]] * [[475]] * [[535]] * [[595]] * [[655]] * [[715]] * [[775]] * [[835]] * [[895]] * [[955]] | * [[1015]] * [[1075]] * [[1135]] * [[1195]] * [[1255]] * [[1315]] * [[1375]] * [[1435]] * [[1495]] * [[1555]] * [[1615]] * [[1675]] * [[1735]] * [[1795]] * [[1855]] * [[1915]] * [[1975]] | * [[2035]] * [[2095]] * [[2155]] * [[2215]] * [[2275]] * [[2335]] * [[2395]] * [[2455]] * [[2515]] * [[2575]] * [[2635]] * [[2695]] * [[2755]] * [[2815]] * [[2875]] * [[2935]] * [[2995]] |}
== Months of the Yin Wood Rabbit == In years where the last digit is 3 or 8 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Wu|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the {{ill|February|ja|2月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of that year is considered a Yin Wood Rabbit month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|ja|啓蟄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Wood Rabbit == === Selection Days === Yin Wood Rabbit days are the third day of the {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} cycle, excluding intervening days. ==See Also== *{{prefix}} *{{intitle}} {{citation needed|きのとう}}
