== Months of the Yin Wood Rabbit == In years where the last digit is 3 or 8 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=}} or {{ill|Wu|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}}), the {{ill|February|ja|2月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/February|qq=}} of that year is considered a Yin Wood Rabbit month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jingzhe|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Wood Rabbit == === Selection Days === Yin Wood Rabbit days are the third day of the {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}} cycle, excluding intervening days. ==See Also== *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
